### Catalog API - HTTP Requests
### Base URLs
@baseUrl_local = http://localhost:5000
@baseUrl_docker = http://localhost:6000
@baseUrl_https_local = https://localhost:5050
@baseUrl_https_docker = https://localhost:6060

### Choose your environment (change @baseUrl to switch)
@baseUrl = {{baseUrl_https_local}}

###############################################
### Product Endpoints
###############################################

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

###

### Get All Products (Verbose - Check if it returns empty array)
# @name getAllProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Product By ID
# @name getProductById
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### NOTE: Replace {{productId}} with an actual GUID from a created product
### Or use the productId from a previous create request

###

### Get Product By ID - Example with Sample GUID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

###

### Get Products By Category
# @name getProductsByCategory
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/Electronics

###

### Get Products By Category - Smartphones
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/Smartphones

###

### Get Products By Category - Laptops
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/Laptops

###

### Get Products By Category - Example with Variable
@categoryName = Electronics
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/{{categoryName}}

###

### Create Product - Test Item (Create this first!)
# @name createTestProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "category": ["Electronics", "Gadgets"],
  "description": "This is a test product to verify the endpoint is working",
  "price": 99.99,
  "imageFile": "test.jpg"
}

###

### Get Product By ID - Use ID from Created Test Product
@testProductId = {{createTestProduct.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{testProductId}}

###

### Create Product - iPhone
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 14 Pro",
  "category": ["Smartphones", "Electronics", "Apple"],
  "description": "Latest Apple smartphone with A16 Bionic chip, Dynamic Island, and Pro camera system",
  "price": 999.99,
  "imageFile": "iphone14pro.jpg"
}

###

### Create Product - Samsung Galaxy
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra",
  "category": ["Smartphones", "Electronics", "Samsung"],
  "description": "Premium Android smartphone with 200MP camera and S Pen",
  "price": 1199.99,
  "imageFile": "galaxys23ultra.jpg"
}

###

### Create Product - MacBook Pro
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MacBook Pro 16-inch M3",
  "category": ["Laptops", "Electronics", "Apple"],
  "description": "Professional laptop with M3 chip, 16-inch Liquid Retina XDR display",
  "price": 2499.99,
  "imageFile": "macbookpro16.jpg"
}

###

### Create Product - Invalid Request (Missing Required Fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "This should fail validation",
  "price": -10.00,
  "imageFile": ""
}

###

### Health Check (if available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Swagger UI (Open in browser)
# Open: {{baseUrl}}/swagger
